title: REPLAY: Fortune Feimster

description:
Original Air Date: March 3, 2021


PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey.

Produced by Melisa D. Monts

 

Kate and Leisha are joined by Fortune Feimster to chat about how she went from entertainment journalist to comedian and actor.
